The paper deals with the formal verification of algorithms, which is a topic that falls under the category of Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO). The use of MapReduce frameworks and distributed algorithms suggests that the paper could also be classified under Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). The use of interactive theorem proving and partial proof automation suggests that the paper could also be classified under Programming Languages (cs.PL) and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
